#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/wall-insulation.html:14
msgid "Are your walls insulated?"
msgstr "Ydy'ch waliau chi wedi'u hinswleiddio?"

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/wall-insulation.html:18
msgid ""
"Cavity walls built before 1991 are typically uninsulated, unless you or "
"someone before you had insulation installed."
msgstr ""
"At ei gilydd, dyw waliau ceudod a adeiladwyd cyn 1991 ddim wedi'u "
"hinswleiddio, oni bai eich bod chi neu rywun cyn chi wedi trefnu i "
"insiwleiddiad gael ei osod."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/wall-insulation.html:22
msgid ""
"Cavity walls built after 1991 were typically built with insulating material "
"between the outer and inner walls."
msgstr ""
"Fel arfer, cafodd waliau ceudod a adeiladwyd ar ôl 1991 eu hadeiladu â "
"deunydd inswleiddio rhwng y waliau allanol a mewnol."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/wall-insulation.html:32
msgid ""
"Homes built after 1991 were typically built with insulating material between "
"the outer and inner walls."
msgstr ""
"Fel arfer, roedd cartrefi ar ôl 1991 yn cael eu hadeiladu gyda deunydd "
"inswleiddio rhwng y waliau allanol a mewnol."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/wall-insulation.html:34
msgid ""
"If your home was converted, for example it was a shop or other commercial "
"premises before, it may have been built without insulation."
msgstr ""
"Os cafodd eich cartref ei drosi, er enghraifft os oedd yn arfer bod yn siop "
"neu safle masnachol arall o'r blaen, efallai ei fod wedi'i godi heb ei "
"inswleiddio."

